column1: Topic title: Umno offering cars  bikes and more prizes at 71st

column8: http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/378773Umno offering cars, bikes and more prizes at 71st anniversary bash11 April 2017Umno is offering cars, bikes and other prizes to mark its 71st anniversary celebration this coming May.Seven cars - including a Proton Perdana - and 10 bikes are up for grabs in a lucky draw open to members and new members who are registered voters on the main celebration day on May 11.Those who want to be in the lucky draw must register to attend the celebrations - to be held at the Bukit Jalil stadium - by May 10.For the rest of this story and more, subscribe for only RM150 a year (full news access)or RM420 a year (full news + full archive access). If you're already a subscriber, please sign in.
It's great that part of my Income Tax contribution ended up there.
